title: Howard Stern Show Aug 04 2010 Wed (The Gayest Week Ever)
description:
This Special Originally aired over 4 days, the 2nd-5th of August in 2010.
I thought I'd share it so that those that are new listeners or have lost their copy of it, May enjoy the craziness that was the stern Show, Before Political correctness took over. For those that have it already, No need to download for no new clips have been added to the special. I'm uploading the days separately.

These are not SternGeeks, though he did give me the idea by posting it & some other Special that I didn't have on his site & might up later which I will give Credit.
